Allrighty, first of all, EndBringer and co. arn't organic. Second of 
all, I just realized that both Rauq and Prodigy have a bot named 
Astrotrain. Can you guys try to work it out between yourselves first 
without me being involved?

::EndBringer/Demise/Greven::

A fairly loud growl originated from Demise at the almost-
shouted "paste some big bots." He looks threateningly at Wildrider, 
but then returns his gaze to Astrotrain and the rest.

EndBringer nods, approaching Astrotrain. "Can you hold all three of 
us?"
